	<!--Name of the mod to display to players-->
	<DisplayName Value="EmergencyPriority" />
	<!--Short description of the mod-->
	<ShortDescription Value="Responding emergency vehicles stop despawning in traffic jams and re-route around congestion." />
	<!--Long description of the mod. Single line or multi line. Supports minimal markdown subset-->
	<LongDescription>
Vanilla Cities Skylines II deletes a responding fire engine, ambulance or police car outright once it is flagged as stuck in traffic, and never re-evaluates its route after dispatch. This mod keeps responding units alive and re-routes them around congestion using the game's own pathfinding.
	</LongDescription>
